metadata.description:
Title: Æ

This NFT is my genesis and is part of me not only photographically but part of my flesh and blood. my daughter is a projection not only of my life but also at the age of nine she is beginning to follow in her father's footsteps, taking photos and starting to create, playing and playing.

Collection: PAPELITOS
Artist: FABIO BORQUEZ
Location: MÖNCHENGLADBACH, GERMANY
1/1 (3333 x 5000px, JPEG), Resolution - 300 ppp
